{"tid":683954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮突宣佈6月課重稅　環球時報：發動「史詩級貿易戰」","createTime":"2018-05-30T06:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T03:40:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":221,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"7182a998b94026e069d89e144c31b2d5cf48dc4d","tid":683954,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:33:09.000Z","msg":"繼上周中美雙方宣佈停止貿易戰後，美國昨（29）日突然宣佈將針對中國進口商品課徵25%關稅，引來中方反彈！中國官媒《環球時報》今（30）日在社論中，批評美國出爾反爾，甚至揚言對美國發動「史詩級貿易戰」。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報在社論中，認為白宮政府目前相當不穩定，出爾反爾幾乎成為常態，強調「如果美方已經決定對中國產品加徵關稅，雙方就不用談了，直接準備打一場『史詩級的貿易戰』就可以了」。<br />\n<br />\n社論也指出，中國一開始就表明不想打貿易戰，但若美國持續施壓，中國也會堅守底線「陪它慢慢玩」，認為美國反悔的行為「不是文明世界的規則」，中國絕對不會容許美國這種「壞習慣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=385912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D385912&d=5MiKebA02DEPhczAPv7l7f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=dd9dadf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D385912&h=c38a2cc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=385912</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a9a0f20772ad4c992868c30d59852cf81b245d","tid":683954,"uid":14816,"like":167,"dislike":2,"score":165,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"環時上次未柒夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"691051408fae70aa16985cc513f32b8d415ba121","tid":683954,"uid":2110,"like":168,"dislike":2,"score":166,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"史詩2個字係咁用架咩"},{"pid":"2b69123ca59e8d3a58f1d7d65243bfdfee2bf20f","tid":683954,"uid":77196,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"鄰國今次想邊間大企業出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9148ede27ec4691fb270f3